<view class="page theory-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <text class="eyebrow">六经治疗发热咳嗽</text>
    <text class="title">看层次、看寒热、看孩子有没有力气</text>
    <text class="muted" wx:for="{{intro}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card model-card">
    <text class="section-title">城堡模型：先把六经想明白</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{modelIntro}}</text>
    <image class="model-image" src="{{modelImage}}" mode="widthFix" bindtap="previewModelImage" show-menu-by-longpress="true"></image>
    <text class="image-hint">点击图片可放大查看</text>
    <view class="model-row" wx:for="{{castleParts}}" wx:key="name">
      <text class="model-name">{{item.name}}</text>
      <text class="model-body">{{item.body}}</text>
      <text class="model-meaning">{{item.meaning}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card relation-card">
    <text class="section-title">六经与阴阳、表里的对应</text>
    <text class="body-text">可以先把六经看成一张地图：太阳在表，少阳在半表半里，阳明、太阴多在里；三阳偏阳、偏热、偏实，三阴更要关注寒、虚、正气和寒热错杂。</text>
    <view class="relation-row" wx:for="{{relations}}" wx:key="channel">
      <view class="relation-head">
        <text class="relation-channel">{{item.channel}}</text>
        <text class="relation-layer">{{item.layer}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="relation-meta">{{item.yinYang}}</text>
      <text class="relation-text">{{item.key}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card model-card">
    <text class="section-title">判断发热咳嗽，先问这三件事</text>
    <view class="question-block" wx:for="{{modelQuestions}}" wx:key="title">
      <text class="question-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="body-text">{{item.text}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card model-card">
    <text class="section-title">为什么同样发热，方向不同？</text>
    <view class="example-block" wx:for="{{modelExamples}}" wx:key="title">
      <text class="question-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="body-text">{{item.text}}</text>
    </view>
    <text class="tip-text">所以六经不是只看体温高低，而是同时看位置、寒热、虚实和孩子整体状态。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card channel-card" wx:for="{{channels}}" wx:key="key">
    <view class="channel-head">
      <text class="channel-title">{{item.title}}</text>
      <text class="tag">{{item.position}}</text>
    </view>
    <image class="channel-image" src="{{item.image}}" mode="widthFix" data-src="{{item.image}}" bindtap="previewChannelImage" show-menu-by-longpress="true"></image>
    <text class="image-hint">点击图片可放大查看</text>
    <text class="field-title">常见线索</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{item.summary}}</text>
    <text class="field-title">发热咳嗽中怎么看</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{item.feverCough}}</text>
    <text class="field-title">治疗方向</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{item.treatment}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="card notice">
    <text class="field-title">安全提示</text>
    <text class="body-text">小于3个月发热、呼吸困难、抽搐、意识异常、明显脱水、精神很差、发热超过3天不缓解等情况，应及时就医。</text>
  </view>
</view>
